snippet: Inbee Park made two long birdie putts on the back nine Saturday and finished with a three-under-par 68 to remain a stroke ahead through the third round of the Meijer L.P.G.A. Classic.
abstract: Inbee Park retains lead in third-round of Meijer LPGA Classic golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Inbee Park made two long birdie putts on the back nine Saturday and finished with a three-under-par 68 to remain a stroke ahead through the third round of the Meijer L.P.G.A. Classic.

headline.main: Two Late Birdies Help Park Stay in Front
